---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import CloudinaryImage from '../components/CloudinaryImage.astro';
---

<Layout title="About" description="A Bronco blog from Hurricane, Utah" currentPage="/about">
  <!-- HERO IMAGE -->
  <section class="about-hero">
    <CloudinaryImage 
      publicId="canyonlands_mapksj"
      alt="About Redford Bronco" 
      gravity="custom"
      class="hero-img" 
    />
    <div class="breadcrumb">
      <a href="/">Home</a>
      <span>/</span>
      <span>About</span>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ABOUT CONTENT -->
  <article class="about-content">
    <h1>About Redford Bronco</h1>
    
    <p>This is a personal blog documenting adventures in and around Hurricane, Utah with our 2025 Ford
    Bronco Badlands. We don't know what we're doing.</p>

    <p>Redford came about because the Bronco Off-Roadeo site wanted a 'nickname' for the vehicle. There seemed to be
    dozens of 'Clifford' ones, because that's the first thing I thought of. After kicking around some ideas, 'Redford' came up
    and that's what we're going with.</p>
    
    <p>No sponsored content. No affiliate links. Just one Bronco, Southern Utah trails, and the occasional mods in the driveway.</p>

    <h2>The Rig</h2>
    
    <p>2025 Ford Bronco Badlands Sasquatch in Ruby Red Metallic with color-matched hardtop. HOSS 3.0 suspension, 35-inch Goodyear Territory MTs, and Raptor running boards.</p>

    <h2>The Mission</h2>
    
    <p>Document every trail we try, every interesting mod, every mistake. Build a resource for other Bronco owners in the Southwest who want to know what actually works on red rock and sand.</p>
  </article>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about-hero {
    position: relative;
    height: 420px;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: var(--surface2);
  }

  .about-hero :global(.hero-img) {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .breadcrumb {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 24px;
    left: 24px;
    z-index: 2;
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 9px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    color: var(--text);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    background: rgba(10,8,7,0.8);
    backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    padding: 8px 16px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(237,232,224,0.2);
  }
  
  .breadcrumb a {
    color: var(--text);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }
  
  .breadcrumb a:hover {
    color: var(--red);
  }
  
  .breadcrumb span {
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  .about-content {
    max-width: 780px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 64px 24px 80px;
  }

  .about-content h1 {
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 900;
    font-size: clamp(52px, 7vw, 72px);
    line-height: 0.95;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .about-content h2 {
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: 32px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    margin: 48px 0 16px;
    color: var(--red);
  }

  .about-content p {
    font-size: 17px;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-hero {
      height: 320px;
    }
    .about-content {
      padding: 48px 16px 60px;
    }
  }
</style>
